/* Deploy postgres to Heroku */
1. Change your prisma .env file to local db
2. Delete prisma/migrations folder
Run: yarn migrate-preview
    to start a new migration

3. Change your prisma .env file back to development db
4. Update migration name in "apply-migration" script in package json
5. Run: yarn apply-migration
6. Run: yarn prisma-reset
7. Run: yarn prisma push
